						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken hero-stone lying near the temple of Ḍoḷḷēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record registers a grant of land made to <hi rend="bold">Bīrabōva</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Tribhuvanasimgi</hi> and the <hi rend="italic">Gauḍas</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Kōḷūr.</hi> The characters are of about the <hi rend="bold">12-13th century A.D.</hi></p>						

